阿姆将制作关于斯坦文化的新纪录片https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-to- Produce-new-documentary-on-stan-culture-3587695?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=eminem-to- Produce-new-documentary-on-斯坦文化Surej SinghThu, 15 Feb 2024 03:54:20 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3587695 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手无意中用他 2000 年的同名歌曲创造了“Stan”这个词</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-to-produce-new-documentary-on-stan-culture-3587695">后阿姆制作的关于斯坦文化的新纪录片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/eminem@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆</a>将根据他的狂热粉丝共同制作一部新纪录片<em>《斯坦斯》</em> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/emimem-music-to-be-murdered-by-review-shock-rapper-continues-to-grow-old-disgracefully-2598079">埃米纳姆：“被谋杀的音乐”评论：震撼说唱歌手继续不光彩地变老</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/eminem-stans-documentary-superfans-1235910241/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，这位说唱歌手即将推出的纪录片以他在 2000 年与 Dido 合作的同名歌曲中创造的术语命名。在这首歌中，阿姆从一位妄想粉丝的角度进行说唱，他认为自己与说唱歌手有着超社会关系。</p><p>根据<em>Variety</em>的报道， <em>《斯坦斯》</em>将是一次“通过世界上最具标志性和最持久的艺术家之一埃米纳姆和崇拜他的粉丝的镜头，进入超级粉丝世界的一次揭露性的、前卫的、令人心平气和的个人之旅。” </p><figure id="attachment_3545791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3545791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3545791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/eminem@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3545791" class="wp-caption-text">阿姆。图片来源：Theo Wargo/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>阿姆的长期经纪人保罗·罗森伯格在谈到这部纪录片时说道：“<em>斯坦斯</em>将为我们提供一个机会，让我们转动镜头，询问观众如何成为粉丝——在某些情况下，成为狂热分子。”这是通过阿姆最迷人的歌曲之一和世界上最重要的艺人之一的镜头来研究粉丝群和艺术家之间的关系。”</p><p>阿姆将在他的 Shady Films 旗下联合制作这部纪录片，史蒂文·莱卡特担任导演。上映日期尚未公布，但这部电影预计在今年晚些时候上映。</p><p>在其他新闻中，埃米纳姆最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-reignites-benzino-feud-on-new-song-doomsday-pt-2-3578318">在他的新歌“Doomsday Pt 2”中重新点燃了与 Benzino 的不和</a>。这首歌重新点燃了埃米纳姆与 2000 年代中期<em>《The Source》</em>杂志前出版商和偶尔说唱歌手之间的不和，并看到他嘲笑 Benzino 的财务状况和外貌。</p><p>在其他地方，这位“爱你说谎的方式”说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-requests-protective-order-against-real-housewives-stars-in-trademark-dispute-case-3563978">请求对<em>《波托马克的真正主妇》</em>明星吉泽尔·布莱恩特和罗宾·迪克森颁发保护令</a>，作为去年正在进行的商标纠纷的一部分。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-to-produce-new-documentary-on-stan-culture-3587695">后阿姆制作的关于斯坦文化的新纪录片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
